parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the TIPM can cause a range of electrical issues, including horn malfunction, windshield wiper malfunction, door lock malfunction, and other electrical system failures, which can lead to accidents, injuries, or strandings.
symptoms: Horn honking randomly
windshield wipers turning on and off
door locks locking and unlocking randomly
lights flashing
and other electrical system malfunctions.
